Description: 
United States Pacific campaign against Japan - one of the most dramatic episodes of the Second World War. Just being in the midst of historic battles, it is possible to estimate the true extent and significance of the battles that took place away from the main fronts of the Great War. 
The player will become a direct participant of the cruel fights and test himself in this battle! 
Extras. Information: Authentic weapons and equipment from the Second World War. 
Historical battles that changed the map of the world: the Philippine operation, Battle of Midway Atoll, the battle for Guadalcanal, and others. 
Encyclopaedic information from all stages of the Pacific campaign of 1941-45 biennium.
